{
  "text": "The assembly module was run with default parameters for each sample. Assemblies, annotations, and all assembly summary statistics were computed in under an hour, using approximately 40 gigabytes (GB) of RAM. Consistent with previous findings [CITATION_1] ) the CISA integrated contigs produced superior assemblies in terms of N50, contig length, and number of contigs in nearly all samples (see Table 1 ).",
  "citation_candidates": [
